heading: Aldurwood Dungeon Guide
content: Aldurwood is an excellent dungeon that's short and easy to complete -- it's even easier for groups who can split farm the Aldurkin objective! The 3 guaranteed Suppressor elite monsters might be a challenge for some ranged builds, but if you come prepared they can easily be blasted down. The offer a good boon for Summoner Necromancers, should you go that path. Save your Sigils: You will want to run this one over and over again as you grow in power! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
